ways dabble in the <em>same</em> gutter.&nbsp;<a href='/s/40290.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(6) Lightning never strikes twice in the <em>same</em> place.&nbsp;<a href='/s/48007.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(7) A man cannot whistle and drink at he <em>same</em> time.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42464.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div id="ad_marginbottom_0" style="margin-top:-10px;margin-bottom:5px;"><script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script><!-- 728_90_20170421 --><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:728px;height:90px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-7200850114163593" data-ad-slot="2392632666"></ins><script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script></div><div>(8) Serve somebody with the <em>same</em> sauce.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43675.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(9) A book is the <em>same</em> today as it always was and it will never change.&nbsp;<a href='/s/40259.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(10) You cannot flay the <em>same</em> ox twice.&nbsp;<a href='/s/44232.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(11) Two students were penalized very differently for the <em>same</em> offence.</div><div>(12) The two houses were built after the <em>same</em> model.</div><div>(13) They had both arrived at the <em>same</em> conclusion.</div><div>(14) Several people in the office are after the <em>same</em> job.</div><div>(15) You should allocate the <em>same</em> amount of time to each question.</div><div>(16) As actress Jane is not in the <em>same</em> class as Susan.</div><div>(17) A true man and a thief think not the <em>same</em>.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42506.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(18) The more things change[sentence dictionary], the more they stay the <em>same</em>.&nbsp;<a href='/s/48102.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(19) Smokers and nonsmokers can not be equally free in the <em>same</em> railway carriage.&nbsp;<a href='/s/47067.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(20) For me the different religions are beautiful flowers from the <em>same</em> garden, or they are branches of the same majestic tree. Therefore they are equally true, though being received and interpreted through human instruments equally imperfect.&nbsp;<a href='/s/47210.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(21) It is my own fault if I am deceived by the <em>same</em> man twice.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43173.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(22) To mention the wolf's name is to see the <em>same</em>.&nbsp;<a href='/s/44035.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(23) A man can not spin and reel at the <em>same</em> time.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42462.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(24) Things of a kind come together; people of a kind fall into the <em>same</em> group.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43979.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(25) A good book is the best of friends, the <em>same</em> today and forever.&nbsp;<a href='/s/40340.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(26) It is a silly fish that is caught twice with the <em>same</em> bait.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41253.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>(27) We should group together all the books by the <em>same</em> author.</div><div>(28) I can find no appreciable differences in the witnesses'descriptions of the accident, they seem the <em>same</em>.</div><div>(29) Women's salaries are low vis-a-vis what men earn for the <em>same</em> work.</div><div style="margin-bottom:3px;">(30) Regardless of how often I correct him, he always makes the <em>same</em> mistake.</div></div><!--all结束-->  <!--如果不是仅显示学生,或该页没有学生句子-->  <div id="student" style='display:none;'>  <div>(1) Two students were penalized very differently for the <em>same</em> offence.</div><div>(2) The two houses were built after the <em>same</em> model.</div><div>(3) Do you still live at the <em>same</em> address?</div><div>(4) It's all the <em>same</em> to me.</div><div>(5) I don't mind whether we eat now or this evening, it's all the <em>same</em> to me.</div><div>(6) My brother's wife and I both had babies around the <em>same</em> time, so the cousins are very close in age.</div><div>(7) The <em>same</em> heavy, brooding silence descended on them.</div><div>(8) All salespeople seem to have the <em>same</em> phoney smile.</div><div>(9) The two books were the <em>same</em> size.</div><div>(10) Can the human race carry on expanding and growing the <em>same</em> way that it is now?</div><div>(11) I resigned last Frid